images.alt: A whimsical yet eerie kitty cat–Xenomorph hybrid, blending adorable feline features—big glowing eyes, soft whiskers, and tiny paws—with sleek, biomechanical alien armor plating and a glossy, elongated head. The creature perches playfully on a control console aboard a dimly lit spaceship interior, the background filled with glowing panels, flickering warning lights, and cold metallic corridors stretching into darkness. Its tail curls with both catlike curiosity and alien menace, tipped with a sharp, reflective barb. The environment glistens with polished steel and faint condensation, catching glimmers of neon blue and red emergency lights. The overall mood is cool, glossy, and darkly futuristic, balancing the cute mischievous charm of a space kitten with the ominous, detailed design of a Xenomorph. Ultra-detailed textures highlight every surface—fur blending into biomechanical plating, glossy reflections, and atmospheric depth with subtle haze. Cinematic lighting enhances the dual nature: part adorable, part menacing.
